description: Categorizes how GridWorks messages are sent and decoded/encoded

value_descriptions.RabbitJsonDirect: Serialized Json message sent on the world rabbit broker from one GNode actor to another
value_descriptions.RabbitJsonBroadcast: Serailized Json message broadcast on the world rabbit broker by a GNode actor
value_descriptions.RabbitGwSerial: GwSerial protocol message sent on the world rabbit broker
value_descriptions.MqttJsonBroadcast: Serialized Json message following MQTT topic format, sent on the world rabbit broker
